    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>chives</strong> finely</p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped chives</strong> in a bowl with your <strong>soured cream</strong>, the juice of <strong>half </strong>your <strong>lemon[s]</strong>, the <strong>remaining grated garlic </strong>(not a big garlic fan? Try using less!)<strong> </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>soured cream & chive dip</strong></p>",
