    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and chop your <strong>brown onion[s] </strong>into discs (roughly 0.5cm thick)</p><p>Tip: Pop out the centres so that you have different sized discs!</p><p>Add the <strong>onion discs </strong>to a bowl with 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> and give everything a good mix up so they are well coated – these are your <strong>floured onions</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and roughly shred</p>",
      "order": 4,
